{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC16_RAN_060.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1c,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Wow, what a beautiful melody...<CR>This has to be Ranun."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hello, Ranun. You seem to be doing well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Did you quit your job with Ernie?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Of course. I cannot continue to suffer through such a bitter experience."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I waited for my chance, and made my escape. I'm not cut out to do labor."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I-I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x188,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I've done all the labor I can stand for the rest of my life. I've already done my best."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x18a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I'd like to continue seeking music in my own way."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, well I think that really suits you, Ranun."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I wonder if it's thanks to Ernie that you can play again..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I don't want to admit it...but my experience with him has introduced me to an all-new kind of music."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "This world is not all sweet nectar.<CR>At times, you need to drink bitter<CR>medicine."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "It's good that I was able to learn that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Hmhm, Ranun, your sense of values is very unique."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x188,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "In any case, I wonder what Ernie wants to accomplish by working so hard..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x18b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Wake up early in the morning, work, eat lunch, work... He even works at night..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x18f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I wonder if he enjoys a life of doing nothing but work..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I think Ernie cherishes his job as much as you cherish your music."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Ernie takes pride in his job."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x18a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Even so, it's far beyond my understanding. I'm sure money isn't everything in this world."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "That may be true, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x157,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Oh...? Hrgh, shoot! I can hear Ernie's carriage!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "The s-sound of his carriage?<CR>I don't hear anything..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x159,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "No, it's no mistake. My hearing is far superior to normal people's."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Being loved by the gods of music isn't just for show."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x15,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I'll be pulled back into the world of Ernie's job."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x19f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "I must escape into the sky! I'll see you later, Ayesha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Oh, okay... <CR>The sky...?"
        }
    ]
}